"{\n  \"correct\": \"no\",\n  \"explanation\": \"The code is using sns.FacetGrid.map() with sns.lmplot(), which is incorrect. sns.lmplot() is a figure-level function and should not be used with sns.FacetGrid.map(). The map() function in FacetGrid is used to apply a function to each facet, but lmplot() is not designed to be used in this way.\",\n  \"patch\": \"5,7c5,7\\n< g = sns.FacetGrid(data=tips, col='time', row='sex')\\n< g.map(sns.lmplot, 'total_bill', 'tip')\\n---\\n> g = sns.lmplot(data=tips, x='total_bill', y='tip', col='time', row='sex')\\n\"\n}"